data.title: Lucas College and Graduate School of Business
data.text:
President's and Dean's Scholars

Congratulations Spring and Fall 2023 Honor Students!

Matriculated, enrolled, undergraduate students who earned an SJSU GPA of 4.0 in Spring or Fall 2023 are recognized as President's Scholars (click here for the list.)

Matriculated, enrolled, undergraduates who earned an SJSU GPA of 3.65 or higher in Spring or Fall 2023 are recognized as Dean's Scholars (see list below.)

Honor roll status is shown on the student's official transcript and is the only form to formally recognize this status.
